要取得USB token设备上的证书并在iText7上签名，您可以使用Java Cryptography Architecture (JCA)提供的API和Bouncy Castle库来实现。下面是一个简要的步骤和示例代码：

1. 导入Bouncy Castle库和iText7库

```java
import org.bouncycastle.jce.provider.BouncyCastleProvider;
import com.itextpdf.text.*;
import com.itextpdf.text.pdf.*;
import java.io.*;
import java.security.*;
import java.security.cert.*;
import java.util.*;
import org.bouncycastle.cert.*;
import org.bouncycastle.cert.jcajce.*;
import org.bouncycastle.cms.*;
import org.bouncycastle.cms.jcajce.*;
import org.bouncycastle.operator.*;
import org.bouncycastle.operator.jcajce.*;
```

2. 配置Bouncy Castle库

```java
Security.addProvider(new BouncyCastleProvider());
```

3. 初始化KeyStore

```java
KeyStore keyStore = KeyStore.getInstance("PKCS11", "SunPKCS11-<path-to-pkcs11-conf-file>");
keyStore.load(null, "<password>".toCharArray());
```

4. 获取证书并构建证书链

```java
Certificate[] certChain = keyStore.getCertificateChain("<alias>");
X509Certificate[] chain = new X509Certificate[certChain.length];
for (int i = 0; i < certChain.length; i++) {
    byte[] encoded = certChain[i].getEncoded();
    ByteArrayInputStream bis = new ByteArrayInputStream(encoded);
    CertificateFactory cf = CertificateFactory.getInstance("X.509");
    chain[i] = (X509Certificate) cf.generateCertificate(bis);
}
```

5. 构建签名私钥

```java
PrivateKey privateKey = (PrivateKey) keyStore.getKey("<alias>", "<password>".toCharArray());
```

6. 构建PDF签名

```java
PdfReader pdfReader = new PdfReader("<path-to-source-pdf>");
ByteArrayOutputStream outputStream = new ByteArrayOutputStream();
PdfStamper pdfStamper = PdfStamper.createSignature(pdfReader, outputStream, '\0');
PdfSignatureAppearance pdfSignatureAppearance = pdfStamper.getSignatureAppearance();

pdfSignatureAppearance.setReason("<reason>");
pdfSignatureAppearance.setLocation("<location>");
pdfSignatureAppearance.setSignDate(new GregorianCalendar());

ExternalDigest digest = new BouncyCastleDigest();
ExternalSignature signature = new PrivateKeySignature(privateKey, "SHA-256", "BC");

MakeSignature.signDetached(pdfSignatureAppearance, digest, signature, chain, null, null, null, 0, MakeSignature.CryptoStandard.CMS);
```

7. 写出PDF文件

```java
byte[] signedPDF = outputStream.toByteArray();
FileOutputStream fos = new FileOutputStream("<path-to-signed-pdf>");
fos.write(signedPDF);
fos.close();

pdfReader.close();
pdfStamper.close();
outputStream.close();
```

