```

4. Initialize these variables in `WinMain()` before entering the message loop:

```cpp
std::srand(std::time(nullptr));
birdX = 50;
birdY = 200;
birdVelocity = 0;
pipeX = 400;
pipeGapY = 200;
windowsHeight = windowHeight; // You should get the window's height during initialization

